Dale Fuller (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dale_Fuller_(actress) 0 Dale Fuller (June 17, 1885 – October 14, 1948) was an American actress of the silent era. She appeared in 67 films between 1915 and 1935. She was born in Santa Ana, California and died in Los Angeles County, California.
